      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s in showroom-perfect condition and has been my absolute pride and joy\u2014I've babied it since day one! Not a single scratch or smudge to be found, and it drives just as smooth as the day I bought it. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that looks and feels brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you. Come by and take a look, I promise you\u2019ll fall in love at first sight!",
      "price": 45900.0,
