    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a peerless 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo, a definitive A80 specimen maintained to concours standards. This vehicle features the iconic 2JZ-GTE 3.0L inline-six engine, utilizing its original sequential twin-turbocharger configuration and factory-spec intercooling system. Power is managed via the robust Getrag V160 six-speed manual gearbox and delivered through a Torsen limited-slip differential. The chassis retains its factory-engineered double-wishbone suspension geometry with zero bushing compliance issues. Every mechanical interface, from the four-piston front calipers to the untouched wiring harness, remains in exemplary condition. This is a rare, unmodified example for the discerning collector who prioritizes mechanical purity and forced-induction precision.",
